                .item
                       a#one(href="${require('./images/work/1.png')}" data-caption="<h2>Sun Life e-newsletters</h2><p>As a Digital Designer in Individual Marketing at Sun Life Financial, my responsibilities include designing and developing IBM Watson Campaign Automation templates for monthly deployment to over ten thousand wholesale advisors and financial centres nationwide. These e-mails inform regulatory changes and provide tips to strengthen relationships between advisors and their clients. Analytics and feedback including conversion rates were used to design more effective marketing communications.</p><p>A recurring design theme was to promote the financial strength and competitive advantage of Sun Life’s Money for Life, a wholistic financial and insurance advice to support every lifestyle and business requirements of individuals, small businesses, and corporations.</p>" data-fancybox="gal")
