                .item
                    a#two(href="${require('./images/work/2.png')}"  data-caption="<h2>Sun Life Illustrations UI</h2><p>Sun Life Illustrations is a tool used for advisors to estimate insurance premiums by product and client data such as age, gender, and insurance coverage. A separate UI was designed for Sun Life’s wealth products, allowing Sun Life advisors to analyze based on asset allocation on different segregated funds and their return based on given market conditions.</p><p>Working with the UX and a team of third party developers at Equisoft, months of user testing and feedback was incorporated to continually refine the wireframes and design of the interface for each desktop and Web release.</p>" data-fancybox="gal")
