                .item
                    a#three(href="${require('./images/work/3.png')}" data-caption="<h2>Sun Life Illustrations reports</h2><p>With a click of a button, the Sun Life Illustrations app can automatically generate PDF reports for advisors to present details of their client’s illustrations. My responsibility is to create InDesign mockups of reports for the Sun Life product portfolio (insurance and wealth) with feedback from advisors, product owners, the Illustrations team, and Equisoft.</p><p>This is to ensure all required copy, tables, and diagrams are presented in an easy-to-read, logical, and concise manner, while minimize printing costs.</p>" data-fancybox="gal")
