                .item
                    a#four(href="${require('./images/work/4.png')}" data-caption="<h2>Sun Life GIF Solutions client statements</h2><p>I was commissioned to design paper statements for clients of Sun Life’s suite of wealth products. Working in collaboration with advisors, product owners, and IFDS (International Financial Data Services), I ensured tables, diagrams and other design deliverables were up to specifications while minimizing costs. The objective was to make sure clients easily understand their financial standings presented in these paper statements mailed semiannually.</p>" data-fancybox="gal")
