                    a#five(href="${require('./images/work/5.png')}" data-caption="<h2>hyperCONNECT</h2><p>Mockups of an Android OS app, hyperCONNECT by Pravala Networks, were developed to seamlessly and transparently move mobile traffic between mobile and WiFi networks. The connection manager allows the user to experience faster, more reliable Internet experience by selecting which networks each app can use. As an added benefit, hyperCONNECT can control data costs or combine 3G/LTE with WiFi networks for lightning fast data transfers.</p>" data-fancybox="gal")
